properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 9 at 2:52AM CST until February 9 at 9:00PM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
...MODERATE TO HEAVY SNOW WILL IMPACT TRAVEL TODAY...

* WHAT...Snow. Total snow accumulations of 2 to 4 inches.

* WHERE...Walworth, Racine, and Kenosha Counties.

* WHEN...From 9 AM this morning to 9 PM CST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Snow covered roads and reduced visibility may create
difficult driving conditions.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Be prepared to allow extra time to reach
your destination.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

The latest road conditions for the state you are calling from can
be obtained by calling 5 1 1.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM THIS MORNING TO 9 PM CST THIS EVENING
